336
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:56,181
Stop!

337
00:16:57,224 --> 00:16:58,308
What's that?

338
00:16:58,392 --> 00:16:59,601
Right there!

339
00:17:00,352 --> 00:17:02,813
Right there!
There's something in his hand.

340
00:17:02,896 --> 00:17:04,606
