507
00:28:15,944 --> 00:28:18,571
I don't know! How am I supposed to know?

508
00:28:19,197 --> 00:28:20,198
You ran after him.

509
00:28:21,741 --> 00:28:24,619
I mean, he was running,

510
00:28:24,703 --> 00:28:26,037
